    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Aumente o desempenho do Mac Removendo efeitos de animação]]></title>
    <link href="http://PauloLuan.github.io//github/blog/2013/11/07/aumente-o-desempenho-do-mac-removendo-efeitos-de-animacao/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-07T17:17:00+00:00</updated>
    <id>http://PauloLuan.github.io//github/blog/2013/11/07/aumente-o-desempenho-do-mac-removendo-efeitos-de-animacao</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Utilize os comandos abaixo para remover os efeitos do Mac e aumentar o seu desempenho.</p>

<!-- more -->




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># opening and closing windows and popovers</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSAutomaticWindowAnimationsEnabled -bool <span class="nb">false</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># smooth scrolling</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSScrollAnimationEnabled -bool <span class="nb">false</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># showing and hiding sheets, resizing preference windows, zooming windows</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c"># float 0 doesn&#39;t work</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSWindowResizeTime -float 0.001
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># opening and closing Quick Look windows</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g QLPanelAnimationDuration -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># rubberband scrolling (doesn&#39;t affect web views)</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSScrollViewRubberbanding -bool <span class="nb">false</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># resizing windows before and after showing the version browser</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c"># also disabled by NSWindowResizeTime -float 0.001</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSDocumentRevisionsWindowTransformAnimation -bool <span class="nb">false</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># showing a toolbar or menu bar in full screen</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSToolbarFullScreenAnimationDuration -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># scrolling column views</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write -g NSBrowserColumnAnimationSpeedMultiplier -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># showing the Dock</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-time-modifier -float 0
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-delay -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># showing and hiding Mission Control, command+numbers</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock expose-animation-duration -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># showing and hiding Launchpad</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock springboard-show-duration -float 0
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock springboard-hide-duration -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># changing pages in Launchpad</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.dock springboard-page-duration -float 0
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># at least AnimateInfoPanes</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.finder DisableAllAnimations -bool <span class="nb">true</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c"># sending messages and opening windows for replies</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.Mail DisableSendAnimations -bool <span class="nb">true</span>
</span><span class='line'>defaults write com.apple.Mail DisableReplyAnimations -bool <span class="nb">true</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>killall Dock
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Sources:</p>

<p><a href="http://www.chriswrites.com/2012/01/turn-off-animations-eye-candy-effects-in-mac-os-x-lion/">http://www.chriswrites.com/2012/01/turn-off-animations-eye-candy-effects-in-mac-os-x-lion/</a></p>

<p><a href="http://unsanity.com/haxies/shadowkiller">http://unsanity.com/haxies/shadowkiller</a></p>

<p><a href="http://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/14001/how-to-turn-off-all-the-animation-effect-on-mac-os">http://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/14001/how-to-turn-off-all-the-animation-effect-on-mac-os</a></p>
]]></content>
